aa(lp216
VSome people believe that
p217
aVthis would spread uncontrollably,
p218
aVand that the bacteria would kill everything in its way.
p219
aVThat's not true at all.
p220
aVIt's a natural process. It goes on in nature today,
p221
aVand the bacteria die as soon as we stop feeding them.
