aVSo, there it is \u2014
p223
aVarchitectural anti-desertification structures
p224
aVmade from the desert itself.
p225
aVSand-stopping devices, made from sand.
p226
aVThe world is likely to lose one third of its arable land
p227
aVby the end of the century.
p228
aVIn a period of unprecedented population growth
p229
aVand increased food demands, this could prove disastrous.
